f>{{cite news|title=Jon Brion to Score Judd Apatow’s ‘Trainwreck’|url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2014/12/12/jon-brion-to-score-judd-apatows-trainwreck/|accessdate=December 14, 2014|publisher=filmmusicreporter.com|date=December 12, 2014|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516191527/https://filmmusicreporter.com/2014/12/12/jon-brion-to-score-judd-apatows-trainwreck/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]新鲜度85%，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上45家媒体综评75分，[[影院评分|影院评分]]上观众给出"A-"的评级，获得普遍好评。

北美收获1.1亿美元，全球总计1.395亿美元。

获得[[第73届金球奖|第73届金球奖]]音乐喜剧类最佳影片、音乐喜剧类最佳女主角（Amy Schumer）两项提名。

== 枪击案 ==
{{main|2015年拉法叶市枪击案}}
2015年7月23日，[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[拉法叶|拉法叶]]一家名叫{{lang|en|The Grand 16 Theater}}的电影院发生枪击案，事发时正放映《生活残骸》<ref name=washington-post-layfayette-louisiana-shooting>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/07/23/gunman-opens-fire-on-la-movie-theater-injuring-several-before-killing-himself/|title=Gunman opens fire on La. movie theater, injuring several before killing himself|first=Sarah|last=Kaplan|work=The Washington Post|date=2015-07-23|accessdate=2015-07-24|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724084033/http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/07/23/gunman-opens-fire-on-la-movie-theater-injuring-several-before-killing-himself/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。59岁的枪手约翰·拉塞尔·豪泽（{{lang|en|John Russell Houser}}）在放映厅内开火<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33654509|title=Louisiana cinema shooting: Lafayette gunman 'had violent past'|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-07-24|accessdate=2015-07-24|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034617/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33654509|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/lafayette-louisiana-movie-theater-gunman-idd-john-russell/story?id=32653062|title=Lafayette, Louisiana, Movie Theater Gunman ID'd as John Russell Houser, 59, of Alabama|publisher=ABC News|date=2015-07-24|accessdate=2015-07-24|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112010742/https://abcnews.go.com/US/lafayette-louisiana-movie-theater-gunman-idd-john-russell/story?id=32653062|dead-url=no}}</ref>，造成2人死亡，9人受伤，最终他吞枪自杀<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/police-theater-gunman-was-drifter-who-planned-to-escape/ar-AAdqs49|title=Wife filed 2008 protective order on theater gunman|publisher=MSN|date=2015-07-24|accessdate=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724212709/http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/police-theater-gunman-was-drifter-who-planned-to-escape/ar-AAdqs49|archive-date=2015-07-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/california/la-me-todays-headlines-html-20150724-htmlstory.html|title=Today: Deadly Rampage in Louisiana Theater.|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2015-07-24|accessdate=2015-07-24|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129041511/https://www.latimes.com/local/california/la-me-todays-headlines-html-20150724-htmlstory.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。舒默和影片发行方[[环球影业|环球影业]]均发表声明，向受害者表示哀悼<ref>{{cite news|first=Tara|last=Fowler|title=Amy Schumer Says Her 'Heart Is Broken' over Trainwreck Shooting That Left 3 Dead and 9 Wounded|url=http://www.people.com/article/trainwreck-shooting-amy-schumers-heart-is-broken|accessdate=2015-07-24|work=People|date=2015-07-24|archive-date=2018-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813071323/https://people.com/article/trainwreck-shooting-amy-schumers-heart-is-broken/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=maane>{{cite news|last=Khatchatourian|first=Maane|title=Universal, Louisiana Theater Owner Respond to ‘Trainwreck’ Shooting, ‘Senseless Tragedy’|date=2015-07-24|work=Variety|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/trainwreck-shooting-universal-reacts-1201548111/|accessdate=2015-07-29|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125095616/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/trainwreck-shooting-universal-reacts-1201548111/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。悲剧过后，舒默和纽约州参议员[[查克·舒默|查克·舒默]]呼吁实行更严厉的[[枪支管制|枪支管制]]法律。2015年10月，她和侄女在HBO脱口秀节目《Amy Schumer: Live at the Apollo》特辑中采访了枪击案的两位受害者<ref>{{cite news|first=Lindsay|last=Kimble|title=Amy Schumer Continues Her Campaign to End Gun Violence: "We Need A Public Outcry"|url=http://www.people.com/article/amy-schumer-asks-fans-to-write-congress-gun-control|accessdate=2015-11-04|work=People|date=2015-10-26|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105206/http://www.people.com/article/amy-schumer-asks-fans-to-write-congress-gun-control|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

